          "-",
          "5",
          "Low Engagement: Low grades, low activities, No forum threads/posts\n\nAssessment-Focused - low grades: high attempts of assessments, low video interactions, low pageviews\n\nPassive Engagement: Meduim grades, moderate pageviews, low activity on forum\n\nAcitve Engagement: High Engagement, moderate aassessment attempts, high forum participation\n\nAssessment-focused - high grades: High grades, high assessments, low pageviews and video",
          "MOOC designers need to make interactions with forums and/or learning contents more engaging for learners… otherwise these will only be passively used. ",
